  section.section-tertiary.features.text-center
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-12.text-center
          .section-heading
            h2 For Translators
            p.head
              | Being more efficient using locize.
            hr
      .row
        .col-md-12
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  .device-container(style="margin: 0 auto 0;")
                    .device-mockup.macbook_2015.silver
                      .device
                        .screen
                          img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/translationmemory_s.jpg', alt='locize dashboard')
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  h3 Smart translation memory
                  p All the benefits of a translation memory. Reuse translations already done. Lookup used terminology.
                  p Take your translation memory with you exporting it to be used in SDL Trados or other localization tools.
          
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  h3 Incontext Editing
                  p Translate directly in your Website / Application. Every translation is a click away.
                  p Translating from within your context is the best way to understand the context of your translation.
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  .device-container(style="margin: 0 auto 0;")
                    .device-mockup.macbook_2015.silver
                      .device
                        .screen
                          img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/incontext_editor_s.jpg', alt='locize statistics')

      .row
        .col-md-12
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  .device-container(style="margin: 0 auto 0;")
                    .device-mockup.macbook_2015.silver
                      .device
                        .screen
                          img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/compare_s.jpg', alt='locize auditing')
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  h3 Powerful compare tool
                  p Our editor enables you to compare your current segments with any other translated language available.
                  p This enables you to lookup transcreated content from other translators making it more easy to get the translations right.
          
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  h3 Machine translations
                  p Machine translations can't replace human translations but can help you speeding up translations.
                  p Use the machine translations for initial translation and edit the suggested translations to match the needed quality.
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  .device-container(style="margin: 0 auto 0;")
                    .device-mockup.macbook_2015.silver
                      .device
                        .screen
                          img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/mt_s.jpg', alt='locize ordering')


  section.section-secondary.features.text-center(style="padding: 100px 0 0;")
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-12.text-center
          .section-heading
            h2 For Developers
            p.head
              | Less time needed for localization - means more time for programming
            hr
              
              
  section.section-gray#video
    .container
      .row
        .col-xs-10.col-xs-offset-1
          .embed-responsive.embed-responsive-16by9
            iframe.embed-responsive-item(width='1280', height='720', src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/9NOzJhgmyQE?rel=0&controls=0&showinfo=0', frameborder='0', webkitallowfullscreen='', mozallowfullscreen='', allowfullscreen='')

  section.section-secondary.features.text-center
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-12
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  .device-container(style="margin: 0 auto 0;")
                    .device-mockup.macbook_2015.silver
                      .device
                        .screen
                          img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/api_s.jpg', alt='locize api')
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  h3 Powerful API
                  p Build any integration against our API.
                  p Add new translations, add new versions and publish them to our CDN using a simple API call.
                    
          
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  h3 CLI Tool
                  p Integrate our cli tool into your build process.
                  p Download translation files in any format provided by locize using your commandline.
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  .device-container(style="margin: 0 auto 0;")
                    .device-mockup.macbook_2015.silver
                      .device
                        .screen
                          img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/cli_s.jpg', alt='locize commandline')
                    

      .row
        .col-md-12
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  .device-container(style="margin: 0 auto 0;")
                    .device-mockup.macbook_2015.silver
                      .device
                        .screen
                          img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/code_s.jpg', alt='locize code')
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  h3 Add new segments from code
                  p No need to add segments manually. Never leave your editor again to add translations.
                  p Using eg. i18next instrumenting your code for internationalization new segments get added to your locize project automatically.
          
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  h3 Versioning
                  p Versioning is essential in development.
                  p Same goes for your translations. Keep multiple versions of your translations. Keep working on latest while your production translations stay untouched.
              .col-md-6
                .feature-item
                  .device-container(style="margin: 0 auto 0;")
                    .device-mockup.macbook_2015.silver
                      .device
                        .screen
                          img.img-responsive(src='img/screenshots/screen/versioning_s.jpg', alt='locize versioning')


  section#contact.contact.bg-tertiary(i18next-options='{"ns": "common"}')
    .container
      h2 Need some help getting started?
      p Get any questions you may have about integrating locize answered by one of our team members.
      a.btn.btn-outline.btn-xl.page-scroll(href='mailto:support@locize.com') Contact us!
